        "classic “subset check” problem using binary search\n",
        "Check if all elements of arr1 exist in arr2\n",
        "\n",
        "👉 If yes → subset\n",
        "👉 If not → not a subset"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "5V-nsr9OnbW1"
      }
